terior-design-020725-946-01-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe first Birdhouse Modular installation is located on a cliffside site on England’s South Coast and is currently available for guest use.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02.jpg\" alt=\"The Birdhouse Modular by Tree Tents is a customisable, sustainable outdoor structure designed to suit any landscape, ideal for eco-tourism, retreats, or off-grid living.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/modular-birdhouse-tiny-house-interior-design-020725-946-02-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eDesigned for flat-pack delivery, the Birdhouse Modular can be assembled quickly by a small team, often within a single day. This approach helps to reduce construction time and costs while minimizing disturbance to the installation site.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/u